Subject: Re: [VB] Safari's in a Westy

The sliders closest to each front vent window are in the way of the front
cot pole. With the windows closed, I just unscrewed the "butterfly" bolt
from each slider and lifted the slider up to rest on the top of the front
curtain which I had closed up. Installed the cot and worked just fine....

Scott
'67 Westy


